reviews.text: Was waiting for too long, it seems the meal are freshly made. Consider that the toilet is shared with the other restaurant, please reserve lower expectations.

Though the place is busy but service is good and friendly.
French fries is always very fresh@

Standard McDonald's with a nice decór. The upstairs has a number of good seats overlooking the street below. The food is consistent quality as compared with other McDonald's. There is a nice little McCafé as well.

Overall a staple establishment in this part of Mong Kok. Nothing fancy, but you weren't looking to McDonald's for fancy anyway.

I have been visiting this McDonald's many times and I think this is one of the most messiest restaurants I have ever seen. You can say it was caused by the customers but the restaurant should assign someone to clean the upstairs periodically. It is unpleasant to have your dinner in a junk yard!
Great food

reviews.text: 通常都人多到🙄😒冇位座和清潔上一手食物盤😅人手不足😌😧
❤️沙冰超好喝的.❤️
由我初入社會工作，由不環保食肆，到現在帶頭叫環保，你話好笑定不好笑。
朋友在這間店，購了士多啤梨奶昔，平常她也有喝，但今次簡直替她洗腸，幸運地可忍至回家，否則不憾設想😐😓
